OL,3,CSearch for missing capybara continues
OL,4,Cas more sightings reported
OL,6,FSearch efforts for a missing capybara
OL,7,Fin Hampshire are continuing as further
OL,8,Fsightings of the fugitive rodent have
OL,9,Fbeen reported.
OL,11,FSamba, the capybara, has been missing
OL,12,Fsince Monday (March 16) when she and
OL,13,Fher sister, Tango, escaped from a
OL,14,Ftemporary holding enclosure at Marwell
OL,15,FZoo.
OL,17,FTango was swiftly re-captured within
OL,18,Fthe zoo grounds, but her sister
OL,19,Fremains on the run.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
