OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774461962
OL,3,CSearch for missing capybara continues
OL,4,Cas more sightings reported
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Marwell, in an
OL,7,Fupdate shared on Wednesday, said that
OL,8,Fsearch teams were continuing to
OL,9,Fmonitor the waterways around the area
OL,10,Fwhere sightings of Samba have been
OL,11,Freported.
OL,13,FThey added that one new sighting of
OL,14,Fthe capybara in an area similar to
OL,15,Fthose previously reported had been
OL,16,Fregistered on Wednesday.
OL,18,FVideo footage of Samba resting on a
OL,19,Fbank of the River Itchen, near
OL,20,FWinchester, was shared earlier this
OL,21,Fweek by a dog walker.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
