OL,3,CSearch for missing capybara continues
OL,4,Cas more sightings reported
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe spokesperson added that additional
OL,12,Fcamera traps had been laid down and
OL,13,Fthermal drones were continuing to be
OL,14,Fused in the search for Samba.
OL,16,F"We do believe she is still in the
OL,17,Fsame area, but that area is large with
OL,18,Fa lot of water so she could be tucked
OL,19,Finto a riverbed and not easily
OL,20,Fvisible," the spokesperson said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
