OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774461962
OL,3,CSearch for missing capybara continues
OL,4,Cas more sightings reported
OL,6,FThey added that the zoo has received
OL,7,F"relevant permissions" to deploy
OL,8,Fhumane traps, which use melon to tempt
OL,9,FSamba out of hiding.
OL,11,FCapybaras are intelligent, gentle
OL,12,Fanimals, which do not pose a risk to
OL,13,Fthe public, according to the zoo, but
OL,14,Fanyone who spots Samba is strongly
OL,15,Fadvised to not approach or try to
OL,16,Fcapture her by themselves to avoid
OL,17,Fcausing any distress.
OL,19,FInstead, sightings of Samba should be
OL,20,Freported at the earliest opportunity
OL,21,Fusing the hotline 07436 167401.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
